CHAT ASSISTANT EXAMPLES

  `EXAMPLE 1`: Create or select OpenAI resource and model deployments

    ai init

  `EXAMPLE 2`: Create an OpenAI assistant

    ai chat assistant create --name "My Assistant" --instructions "You are a helpful Assistant."

  `EXAMPLE 3`: Upload files for use with RETRIEVAL

    ai chat assistant file upload --files **\*.md

  `EXAMPLE 4`: Create an OpenAI assistant w/ RETRIEVAL for specific files, and chat with it

    ai chat assistant create --name "My Assistant 2" --instructions "You are a helpful Assistant." --file-ids ID1 ID2 ...
    ai chat --interactive

  `EXAMPLE 5`: Chat with a previously created assistant

    ai chat assistant list
    ai chat --assistant-id ID --interactive

  `EXAMPLE 6`: Create sample Node.js source code

    ai dev new openai-asst-streaming --javascript

  `EXAMPLE 7`: Create interactive browser javascript source code 

    ai dev new openai-asst-webpage-with-functions --javascript

